high_descs: Go forward and slightly right to the trash canister.
Pick up the pen out of the canister.
Turn around and veer left to the cabinet on the right side of the bed.
Put the pen in the mug on the counter.
Pick up the mug.
Go forward and veer right to the desk.
Put the mug on the desk in front of and to the right of the pencil.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a pen in it on a table.

high_descs: Move to the trash can right of the desk.
Take the pen out of the trash can.
Bring the pen to the night stand on the right of the bed.
Put the pen in the mug on the night stand.
Pick up the mug from the night stand.
Bring the mug to the desk.
Put the mug on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with pen on the desk.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the trash can.
Take the pen out of the trash can.
Turn and walk across the room, hang a left after the bed and go to the nightstand next to the bed.
Put the pen in the coffee cup.
Pick up the coffee cup with the pen in it.
Walk across the room, take a right at the sofa, and go to the desk.
Set the cup with the pen in it down near the front edge of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Take the coffee cup with the pen inside to the desk.
